Revision history for Plack-Middleware-Debug-HTML-Mason

{{$NEXT}}
	Update metadata to include the minimal perl version (5.14).
	
	Set a flag in the psgi env (psgi.middleware.debug.htmlmason) when the
	panel is active.  This is helpful for only loading the plugin when you
	need it.
	
